name: 萝宾·贝特里奇
name_full: 萝宾·贝特里奇 Robyn Betteridge
introduction: Robyn Betteridge is a Young Artist Academy, Award Winning, British Actress born in 2011. She is an actress / model & contortionist signed to Kids London Ltd. Robyn has modeled & performed in commercials for numerous brands and performed contortion in many live shows in London. At age 8 Robyn was cast for 'The Wheel Of Time' which was Robyn's first TV series debut.
